cu.explanation_en: Setting Num_Threads_PUSCH to an out-of-range value (1000) will cause thread allocation failure and PUSCH processing issues.

du.explanation_en: Setting prach_msg1_FrequencyStart to an out-of-range value (1000) will cause invalid PRACH frequency configuration and RACH procedure failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 prach_msg1_FrequencyStart 設定為超出範圍的值 (1000)，會導致無效的 PRACH 頻率配置，並造成 RACH 程序失敗。
